
vdt-build is used to create new native packages for the VDT infrastructure.

It is modelled on Fedora's fedpkg; the ultimate goal is to provide a friendly
interface for contributors to the OSG-Software effort.

It is currently very new; expect much code churn and rewrites in the future.

Documentation can be found at:

https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/SoftwareTeam/RPMDevelopmentGuide

